blog.name: grandma-names-pokemon
blog.title: My grandmother likes to name Pokemon!
blog.description: Hello world! As the title suggests, my grandma likes to name my Pokemon. If you have a ‘mon you’d like for her to name shoot me an ask! If I ever don’t respond to an ask it’s probably because that Pokemon has already been named. I tag everything so just search for a Pokemon to see if it’s been named :) check out my other blog @grandma-names-characters to see the names and personalities of non-pokemon characters!
